high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the white table.
Pick the black bottle up from the table.
Go right, and then right again to stand in front of the fridge.
Put the bottle in the fridge and close the door and then open it and take the bottle out.
Go left and face the cabinet below the sink.
Put the bottle in the lower, left cabinet and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled bottle in a cabinet.

high_descs: Move around to the face the table on your left.
Pick up the wine bottle on the table.
Head right, the go right to the fridge.
Chill the wine bottle in the fridge.
Bring the chilled wine bottle to the sink.
Put the wine bottle in the left cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled wine bottle in the left cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Walk over to the table
Pick up the bottle of wine from the table
Carry it to the fridge
Open up the door and place the bottle of wine inside and shut the door
Open the fridge back up and get the bottle of wine back out
Carry the bottle to the cabinet and open the door and place the bottle of wine in the cabinet
Turn around and find the square white table on the left.
Pick up the glass bottle in the front of the table.
Take the bottle and turn around to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the glass bottle inside. Take the bottle out and shut the door.
Take the bottle and turn left to locate the sink.
Place the bottle in the bottom cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill a bottle and put it away in the cabinet.
